-- China Everbright Bank Plans to List Shares on Shanghai Exchange August 18
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-29T23:25:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/china-everbright-bank-plans-to-list-shares-on-shanghai-exchange-august-18.html

          
          
             China Everbright Bank Co. shares are
scheduled to start trading on the Shanghai Stock Exchange after
an initial public offering, according to a prospectus from the
Chinese lender posted to the Shanghai Stock Exchange.  
 China Everbright will price the shares in the offering on
Aug. 11, the prospectus said. The funds from the offering will
be used to bolster capital, the bank said.  
